{"title":"(13) implementacion-amb-sysmayal2 - Raven","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-implementacion-amb-sysmayal2","summary":"This page documents the Phase 5 completion of the AMB-Wellness smart agent implementation on the Raven messaging system within the ERPNext ERP. The testing verified end-to-end functionality including delivery note creation from sales orders with automatic batch assignment using FIFO logic, and invoice creation with Mexico CFDI compliance (PPD payment terms and G01 goods classification). The smart agent demonstrated advanced capabilities including pre-flight validation for stock/batch warnings, automatic batch assignment compatible with ERPNext v16 Batch.batch_qty, and proper handling of Mexico-specific tax requirements. Phase 2 optimization was completed with 13 files restructured from monolithic code to modular components including cache_layer.py, queue_handlers.py, smart_delivery.py, and others. All test artifacts were successfully rolled back, leaving production data clean. The agent achieved HIGH confidence and LEVEL 2 autonomy. The implementation is now ready for Phase 3.","key_points":["Phase 5 testing completed - Smart agent verified for full E2E pipeline","Delivery Note MAT-DN-2026-00005 created from SO-00763 with 3/3 batches auto-assigned using FIFO","Sales Invoice ACC-SINV-2026-00006 created with Mexico CFDI compliance (PPD payment, G01 goods)","Smart features verified: pre-flight validation, auto batch assignment, CFDI auto-fill, error handling","All test artifacts rolled back - production environment clean","Phase 2 optimization complete - 13 files restructured into modular components","Files organized into workflows.py split (6 modules) and agent.py split (5 modules)","Agent achieved HIGH confidence level and LEVEL 2 autonomy","All 7 Phase 5 tasks completed successfully","Architecture recommendations ARCH-01 through ARCH-04 all marked DONE","Ready for Phase 3 deployment when orchestrator assigns next task","Executive summary shows $0 revenue MTD with 0 orders"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/delivery-note/MAT-DN-2026-00005","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/sales-order/SO-00763-LORAND%20LABORATORIES","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/app/sales-invoice/ACC-SINV-2026-00006","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-marketing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-manufacturing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-batch-lote102"],"file_name":"amb_wellness_phase5_implementation_summary.json"}
